nordic-dark-description =
    Nordic Dark is a calm, focused desktop theme inspired by the Nord color palette.

    It uses muted arctic blues and cool grays as the base, with soft teal accents and
    light snow-white text. Compared to Midnight Blue, Nordic Dark has slightly lower
    contrast and warmer dark tones — ideal for long reading and writing sessions.

nordic-dark-features =
    - Muted arctic blue and gray tones
    - Soft teal accent color
    - Snow-white text on cool dark backgrounds
    - Lower contrast — comfortable for long sessions
    - Inspired by the Nord color palette
